## Stakeholder Mapping Workflow

- [ ] 1. Research the full organizational landscape — who is involved, at what level, and in what capacity
- [ ] 2. Map each stakeholder on an influence/interest grid
- [ ] 3. Document each stakeholder's role, goals, concerns, and relationship to the project
- [ ] 4. Identify hidden stakeholders — those not obviously involved but with influence
- [ ] 5. Assess relationships between stakeholders — alliances, tensions, hierarchies
- [ ] 6. Categorize stakeholders into engagement priority tiers
- [ ] 7. Produce a visual and narrative stakeholder map

## Key Inputs
- Initiative or project: {{initiative}}
- Known stakeholders: {{known_stakeholders}}
- Organization structure (if known): {{org_structure}}
- Objective: {{objective}}
